  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening disaster preparedness and response and community resilience in Sierra Leone</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of this project is to improve the effectiveness of disaster preparedness, response and community resilience in Sierra Leone. This project will take a two-pronged approach to strengthening institutional (national and district level) disaster management capacity and activate Community-Based Disaster Risk Management (CBDRM) to holistically reduce the impact of impending disasters on vulnerable communities.</narrative>
  </description>
